Paper: hep-th/0004107

Date: 2000-04-14

Title: A Realization of the infinite dimensional Symmetries of Conformal

MechanicsAuthors: M. Cadoni, P. Carta, S. Mignemi

Comments: RevTeX file, 10 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D62 (2000) 086002

We discuss the possibility of realizing the infinite dimensional symmetriesof conformal mechanics as time reparametrizations, generalizing the realizationof the SL(2,R) symmetry of the de Alfaro, Fubini, Furlan model in terms ofquasi--primary fields. We find that this is possible using an appropriategeneralization of the transformation law for the quasi-primary fields.